-- ENRC Considering Spin Off African Business, Sunday Times Reports
-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 2012-05-06T12:59:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-06/enrc-working-on-plan-to-spin-off-african-business-times-says.html
Eurasian Natural Resources Corp. (ENRC)  is
working on a plan with Credit Suisse Group AG and Morgan Stanley
to spin off its African business, the Sunday Times reported,
citing people close to the matter.  Eurasian Natural Resources said in an e-mailed statement it
notes the newspaper article. Whilst the company continues to
evaluate various options, no decision has been made, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Biesheuvel in London at 
 tbiesheuvel@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
